<%- include('../layouts/header', { title: title }) %>
<%- include('../partials/navbar') %>

<div class="container mt-5">
    <div class="text-center text-white mb-5">
        <h1 class="display-4 fw-bold gradient-text">Frequently Asked Questions</h1>
        <p class="lead">Pertanyaan yang sering diajukan oleh pengguna</p>
    </div>

    <div class="row justify-content-center">
        <div class="col-lg-8">
            <div class="accordion accordion-flush" id="faqAccordion">
                
                <!-- FAQ Item 1 -->
                <div class="accordion-item bg-dark-secondary border border-secondary mb-3 rounded">
                    <h2 class="accordion-header" id="flush-headingOne">
                        <button class="accordion-button collapsed bg-transparent text-white" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#flush-collapseOne" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="flush-collapseOne">
                            Bagaimana cara upload game?
                        </button>
                    </h2>
                    <div id="flush-collapseOne" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="flush-headingOne" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
                        <div class="accordion-body text-white">
                            Daftar akun, login, lalu klik tombol "Upload Game" di navbar. Isi form detail game dan upload file game Anda.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- FAQ Item 2 -->
                <div class="accordion-item bg-dark-secondary border border-secondary mb-3 rounded">
                    <h2 class="accordion-header" id="flush-headingTwo">
                        <button class="accordion-button collapsed bg-transparent text-white" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#flush-collapseTwo" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="flush-collapseTwo">
                            Apakah game di sini gratis?
                        </button>
                    </h2>
                    <div id="flush-collapseTwo" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="flush-headingTwo" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
                        <div class="accordion-body text-white">
                            Sebagian besar game gratis untuk dimainkan. Namun, developer dapat menetapkan harga untuk game premium mereka.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- FAQ Item 3 -->
                <div class="accordion-item bg-dark-secondary border border-secondary mb-3 rounded">
                    <h2 class="accordion-header" id="flush-headingThree">
                        <button class="accordion-button collapsed bg-transparent text-white" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#flush-collapseThree" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="flush-collapseThree">
                            Metode pembayaran apa yang didukung?
                        </button>
                    </h2>
                    <div id="flush-collapseThree" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="flush-headingThree" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
                        <div class="accordion-body text-white">
                            Kami mendukung QRIS, Virtual Account (BCA, Mandiri, BNI, BRI), dan kartu kredit.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- FAQ Item 4 -->
                <div class="accordion-item bg-dark-secondary border border-secondary mb-3 rounded">
                    <h2 class="accordion-header" id="flush-headingFour">
                        <button class="accordion-button collapsed bg-transparent text-white" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#flush-collapseFour" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="flush-collapseFour">
                            Apakah data akun saya aman?
                        </button>
                    </h2>
                    <div id="flush-collapseFour" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="flush-headingFour" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
                        <div class="accordion-body text-white">
                            Ya, kami menggunakan enkripsi standar industri untuk melindungi data pribadi dan password Anda. Keamanan privasi pengguna adalah prioritas utama kami.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- FAQ Item 5 -->
                <div class="accordion-item bg-dark-secondary border border-secondary mb-3 rounded">
                    <h2 class="accordion-header" id="flush-headingFive">
                        <button class="accordion-button collapsed bg-transparent text-white" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#flush-collapseFive" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="flush-collapseFive">
                            Bagaimana cara melaporkan bug atau game bermasalah?
                        </button>
                    </h2>
                    <div id="flush-collapseFive" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="flush-headingFive" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
                        <div class="accordion-body text-white">
                            Anda dapat menghubungi tim support kami melalui email <a href="mailto:coks.helper@gmail.com" class="text-aqua">coks.helper@gmail.com</a> atau menggunakan fitur "Report" yang tersedia di setiap halaman detail game.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- FAQ Item 6 -->
                <div class="accordion-item bg-dark-secondary border border-secondary mb-3 rounded">
                    <h2 class="accordion-header" id="flush-headingSix">
                        <button class="accordion-button collapsed bg-transparent text-white" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#flush-collapseSix" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="flush-collapseSix">
                            Apakah developer mendapatkan penghasilan?
                        </button>
                    </h2>
                    <div id="flush-collapseSix" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="flush-headingSix" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
                        <div class="accordion-body text-white">
                            Tentu! Kami menawarkan sistem bagi hasil yang kompetitif (70:30) untuk developer yang mempublikasikan game berbayar di platform kami.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- FAQ Item 7 -->
                <div class="accordion-item bg-dark-secondary border border-secondary mb-3 rounded">
                    <h2 class="accordion-header" id="flush-headingSeven">
                        <button class="accordion-button collapsed bg-transparent text-white" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#flush-collapseSeven" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="flush-collapseSeven">
                            Saya lupa password, apa yang harus dilakukan?
                        </button>
                    </h2>
                    <div id="flush-collapseSeven" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="flush-headingSeven" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
                        <div class="accordion-body text-white">
                            Jangan panik. Silakan akses halaman Login dan klik link "Lupa Password?". Kami akan mengirimkan instruksi reset kata sandi ke email Anda yang terdaftar.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<%- include('../layouts/footer') %>
